{
  "name": "Mystical Powers",
  "pages": [
    {
      "_id": "90c4eec902d3b735",
      "name": "Overview",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Mystical powers in SoHL encompass all supernatural abilities — arcane\nspellcasting, divine miracles, spiritual gifts, and other extraordinary\ncapabilities.</p>\n"
      },
      "_key": "!journal.pages!PlsGHQa9BZ44YwzP.90c4eec902d3b735"
    },
    {
      "_id": "9c24252d160d80a7",
      "name": "Casting Spells and Performing Miracles",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>To use a mystical ability:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open the character's sheet and go to the <strong>Mystery</strong> tab.</li>\n<li>Find the ability you want to use.</li>\n<li>Click the ability name to initiate a test.</li>\n<li>The system resolves the test based on the ability's skill requirements.</li>\n</ol>\n<!-- TODO: Document the full spellcasting workflow — preparation,\n     casting test, fatigue cost, duration, range, and effect resolution.\n     Include how miracles differ from arcane spells. -->"
      },
      "_key": "!journal.pages!PlsGHQa9BZ44YwzP.9c24252d160d80a7"
    },
    {
      "_id": "mystical-devices",
      "name": "Mystical Devices",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>A <strong>Mystical Device</strong> is a magical item that contains mystical abilities.\nEnchanted weapons, holy relics, and magical rings are all mystical devices.\nThe device holds nested Mystical Abilities that the wielder can invoke.</p>\n<p>When a Mystical Device is given to a character (by dropping it onto their\nsheet), its abilities become available on the Mystical tab.</p>\n<!-- TODO: Document how mystical devices interact with the character's\n     own mystical capabilities, attunement requirements, and charges/uses -->"
      },
      "_key": "!journal.pages!PlsGHQa9BZ44YwzP.mystical-devices"
    },
    {
      "_id": "7eb1adb74f775004",
      "name": "The Mystical Tab",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>The Mystical tab on a Being's sheet shows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Mysteries</strong> the character has learned</li>\n<li><strong>Mystical Abilities</strong> available to the character</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- TODO: Document the Mystical tab layout in detail, including how to\n     add/remove mystical capabilities and how the hierarchy is displayed -->"
      },
      "_key": "!journal.pages!PlsGHQa9BZ44YwzP.7eb1adb74f775004"
    }
  ],
